data.description: Under Construction. 100% USDA Financing Available with as little as no out of pocket expenses for closing cost. Beautiful brand new concrete block home with stucco. Modern split plan 3 bedroom 2 bath with attached 2 car garage and covered patio. Wall to wall carpeting in the bedrooms then luxury vinyl plank throughout the rest of the home. Walk in Closet in Master Bedroom. Appliances include Refrigerator, Oven and Range with Microwave hood, and Dishwasher. Photos are not of this home but another the same model built in another location. We have other new homes being constructed in the area as well.
